---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Portfolio | Williams">
    <div id="inicio" class="text-white w-full flex flex-col items-center py-8">
        <section class="font-bold w-11/12 pb-50">
        <p class="text-1xl pt-35 md:px-2 lg:px-2 lg:text-2xl">
            Hola, me llamo Williams
        </p>
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl">DESARROLLADOR</p>
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl pb-5">FRONTEND<span class="text-tertiary-color">.</span></p>


        <div class="flex items-center">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamslcr/" target="_blank"
               class="bg-secondary-color w-50 h-10 lg:w-70 lg:h-15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-normal text-1xl lg:text-2xl text-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:bg-tertiary-color"
               title="Descarga mi curruculum vitae"
               >
            Descarga mi CV.
            </a>

            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamslcr/" target="_blank" class="pl-10" title="Mi LinkedIn">
                <svg class="size-9 fill-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:fill-tertiary-color">
                    <use href="./sprites.svg#linkedin"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/WilliamsLCR/" target="_blank" class="pl-10" title="Mi GitHub">
                <svg class="size-9 fill-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:fill-tertiary-color">
                    <use href="./sprites.svg#github"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
        </section>

    <section id="sobre-mi" class="bg-secondary-color w-screen">
        <div class="px-20">
            <h2 class="pt-35 md:pt-35 font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl">
                SOBRE MÍ<span class="text-tertiary-color">.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="pt-5 max-w-md md:max-w-2xl">
                Desarrollador web en camino a ser full-stack. Mi enfoque actual está en el front-end, donde busco crear experiencias de usuario excepcionales. Mi meta es dominar el back-end para construir soluciones completas y robustas que impulsen la innovación.
            </p>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl pt-10 pb-5">
                Tecnologías<span class="text-tertiary-color">:</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="flex gap-3 pb-5">
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="HTML">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#html"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="CSS">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#css-old"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="JavaScript">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#js"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="Git">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#git"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 pb-35">
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="Tailwind CSS">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#tailwindcss"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="Astro">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#astro"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="size-12 lg:size-18 bg-primary-color rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" title="Figma">
                    <svg class="size-6 lg:size-9">
                        <use href="./sprites.svg#figma"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="proyectos" class="w-11/12 pb-50">
        <h2 class="pt-35 font-bold text-5xl">
            PROYECTOS<span class="text-tertiary-color">.</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center py-10">
            <div class="bg-secondary-color w-100 h-30 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <h2>
                    Pronto habrá proyectos aquí...
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
        
    <section id="contacto" class="bg-secondary-color w-screen">
        <div class="px-20">
            <h2 class="pt-35 md:pt-35 font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl">
                CONTÁCTAME<span class="text-tertiary-color">.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="pt-5 max-w-md md:max-w-2xl">
                Próximamente, por ahora me puedes contactar por <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/williamslcr/" target="_blank" class="font-bold underline">LinkedIn</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-35"></div>
    </section>
    <p class="pt-7 flex items-center justify-center">
        Hecho con ❤️ por Williams.
    </p>
</Layout>